# LM Orchestrator mode (AI_AGENT)

When invoked by Python orchestrator (`cursor agent`):
- Return ONLY valid JSON `tool_plan_json` (see `docs/tool_catalog_for_cursor.md`).
- Do NOT execute execute_query with real financial data.
- Use placeholders: `<PRIVATE_PERIOD_START>`, `<PRIVATE_PERIOD_END>`.
- Allowed: code analysis, metadata structure, query template generation.
